---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Service Areas — Photography Across Texas | Pichardo's Photography"
description: "Pichardo's Photography serves all of Texas — Dallas, Fort Worth, Houston, Austin, El Paso, McAllen, Waco, Tyler, Galveston and more."
permalink: /service-areas/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow animate-up">Where We Go</span>
    <h1 class="animate-up delay-1">Serving All of Texas</h1>
    <div class="gold-line center animate-up delay-2"></div>
    <p style="max-width:600px;margin:1rem auto 0;color:var(--text-muted);" class="animate-up delay-2">
      Based in Dallas, we travel throughout the Lone Star State. No milestone is too important to miss — and no distance is too far.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-3 reveal">
      {% for area in areas %}
      <a href="/service-areas/{{ area.slug }}/" class="area-card" style="display:block;">
        <div style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-radius:var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0 0;margin:-0 -0 1.5rem -0;aspect-ratio:16/9;">
          {% pic area.heroImage, "Photography in " + area.city + ", TX", { widths: [600], sizes: "(max-width: 1024px) 50vw, 33vw", style: "width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;transition:transform 0.5s ease;" } %}
        </div>
        <div class="area-city">{{ area.city }}</div>
        <div class="area-state">Texas</div>
        <ul class="area-landmarks">
          {% for landmark in area.landmarks | slice(0, 3) %}
          <li>{{ landmark }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        <div style="margin-top:1rem;">
          <span style="font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);font-weight:700;">View {{ area.city }} →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
